ss=\"keyword\">if</span>((i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>)%<span class=\"number\">10</span>==<span class=\"number\">0</span>)<span class=\"built_in\">cout</span>&lt;&lt;a[i]&lt;&lt;<span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span>&lt;&lt;a[i]&lt;&lt;<span class=\"string\">' '</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","next":{"title":"凸包面积——Graham扫描法","slug":"凸包面积——Graham扫描法"},"link":"http://starlx.cn/post/合并排序（分治法）/","toc":[{"title":"简介","id":"简介","index":"1","children":[{"title":"1、分","id":"1、分","index":"1.1"},{"title":"2、治(合并相邻有序子序列)","id":"2、治-合并相邻有序子序列","index":"1.2"}]}]}